@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gtbrrc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.09
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.42 - v2 + 0.65)) * (v2 / wp.exp(v1 + 0.94)))
    v2 = ((tmp - wp.cos(v2 + 0.73)) / 0.79)
    data[tid] = v0
